item.dc:creator: @The_Outsider The Outsider
item.description:
@The_Outsider wrote:

This is more than likely because you have a space in the .cfg. You cannot have an stray spaces in that file, period. Do a search for " " (a space) and then remove it. Use your tab only, and a space counts if it’s just the Enter key on a new line.

You don’t need Team Viewer for everything you know.

And stop shouting at me.
